    <title>serverless+travis-ci部署hexo博客</title>
    <link href="https://github.com/leeningzzu/leeningzzu.github.io/2019/03/01/my%20blog/Software%20and%20skillings/skillings/20190301-serverless+travis-ci%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>https://github.com/leeningzzu/leeningzzu.github.io/2019/03/01/my blog/Software and skillings/skillings/20190301-serverless+travis-ci部署hexo博客/</id>
    <published>2019-02-28T19:09:06.000Z</published>
